 - Structure: Object{site_number, type, facility_name, faa_ident, icao_ident, district_office, state, state_full, county, city, ownership, use, manager, manager_phone, latitude, latitude_sec, longitude, longitude_sec, elevation, magnetic_variation, tpa, vfr_sectional, boundary_artcc, boundary_artcc_name, responsible_artcc, responsible_artcc_name, fss_phone_number, fss_phone_numer_tollfree, notam_facility_ident, status, certification_typedate, customs_airport_of_entry, military_joint_use, military_landing, lighting_schedule, beacon_schedule, control_tower, unicom, ctaf, effective_date}
charts_get: Get charts for a specified airport
Parameters: {"apt": "Required. string. FAA or ICAO airport identifier (KAVL or AVL). Separate multiple entries with a comma.", "group": "integer. Optional grouping of the charts. 1 -> General, Departures, Arrivals, Approaches; 2 -> Airport Diagram only; 3 -> General only; 4 -> Departures only; 5 -> Arrivals only; 6 -> Approaches only; 7 -> Everything but General."}
Output: OK.
 - Format: application/json
 - Structure: Object{state, state_full, city, airport_name, military, faa_ident, icao_ident, chart_seq, chart_code, chart_name, pdf_name, pdf_path}
charts_changes_get: Get chart changes by airport or chart name
Parameters: {"apt": "Required. string. FAA or ICAO airport identifier (KAVL or AVL).", "chart_name": "string. Partial or full name of the chart/procedure."}
Output: OK.
 - Format: application/json
 - Structure: Object{state, state_full, city, airport_name, military, faa_ident, icao_ident, chart_seq, chart_code, chart_name, pdf_name, pdf_path}
charts_afd_get: Get the AFD for a specified airport
Parameters: {"apt": "Required. string. FAA or ICAO airport identifier (KCLT or CLT)."}
